Achievements.Name: It Begins With a Ring
Achievements.Description: Ring the mysterious bell. What happens after that, is up to you.

Achievements.Name: Do Not Shoot the Water!
Achievements.Description: Summon the master of the lake. Don't rock the boat.

Achievements.Name: A Rock and a Hard Place
Achievements.Description: Outmaneuver the rampaging beast, El Gigante.

Achievements.Name: Secure the Ballistics
Achievements.Description: Rescue the president's daughter, Ashley. Afterwards, the real fun begins.

Achievements.Name: A Bloodline Severed
Achievements.Description: Defeat the village chief in battle.

Achievements.Name: A Terrifying Assassin
Achievements.Description: Turn the tables on Verdugo, the right hand of Salazar.

Achievements.Name: The Castellan Falls
Achievements.Description: Defeat Salazar, and make your escape from the castle.

Achievements.Name: The Ties That Bind
Achievements.Description: Defeat Krauser, your former partner, in battle.

Achievements.Name: We're Going Home
Achievements.Description: Defeat Saddler in battle, and escape from the nightmare.

Achievements.Name: A Heart of Steel
Achievements.Description: Clear the game on the highest difficulty.

Achievements.Name: What Are They Worth?
Achievements.Description: Acquire all of the bottle caps in the game.

Achievements.Name: The S Stands for Stylish!!
Achievements.Description: Acquire all of the costumes in the game.
